    创建DMS模块

    mdl_create.Rd

    创建DMS模块

    mdl_create(
  mdl_name = "mdlStarNight",
  mdl_dir = "/home/hulilei/mdls/",
  demo_dir = "/home/hulilei/mdls/mdlDemo/",
  demo_name = "mdlDemo",
  type = c("Com", "Pkg", "r", "Server", "UI")
)

    Arguments

    mdl_name

    模块名称

    mdl_dir

    模块目录

    demo_dir

    模板目录

    demo_name

    模板名称

    type

    模板类型

    Value

    返回值
